## 补丁2: proxy.cc - 添加超时检测逻辑

```diff
--- a/src/proxy.cc
+++ b/src/proxy.cc
@@ -45,6 +45,16 @@ NCCL_PARAM(ProxyAppendBatchSize, "PROXY_APPEND_BATCH_SIZE", 16);
 NCCL_PARAM(CreateThreadContext, "CREATE_THREAD_CONTEXT", 0);
 NCCL_PARAM(ProxyDumpSignal, "PROXY_DUMP_SIGNAL", -1);
 NCCL_PARAM(ProgressAppendOpFreq, "PROGRESS_APPEND_OP_FREQ", 8);
