## 补丁4: shm.cc - 更新SHM Transport活跃时间

```diff
--- a/src/transport/shm.cc
+++ b/src/transport/shm.cc
@@ -280,6 +280,9 @@ static ncclResult_t shmSendProxyProgress(struct ncclProxyState* proxyState, str
   if (args->state == ncclProxyOpReady) {
